Hi Greg,

Thanks for your report. I added support for it in the CVS. Please fetch
the files either directly from the CVS, or via the web at this address :
http://cvs.sourceforge.net/viewcvs.py/ddccontrol/ddccontrol-db/db/monitor/ (SAM0191.xml and SAM0192.xml).

Could you try to write 0x04 to control 0xf0 ? It should be a "magic
color" preset, but I don't know which one. Here is the db file part
corresponding to this control :
<control id="magiccolor" type="list" address="0xf0">
	<value id="off" value="0"/>
	<value id="demo" value="1"/>
	<value id="full" value="2"/>
	<value id="intelligent" value="3"/>
</control>

Thanks,

Best regards,

Nicolas

