I'm using a Dell Latitude D610 laptop with a "D/Port Advanced Port 
Replicator", now associated to a Samsung SyncMaster 960BF monitor.

Details for the port replicator are here:
http://accessories.us.dell.com/sna/productdetail.aspx?c=us&l=en&s=dhs&cs=19&sku=310-7704
The port replicator has two video outputs: VGA (Analog) and DVI 
