vanilla-kernel 2.6.15.7. My video card is a Matrox G450 connected to a
SUN-GDM-5410 monitor. I'm trying to use ddcontrol-0.4.1 with ddccontrol-
db-20060308. Compiling went through without any errors. Both monitor and
video car should be supported by ddcontrol-0.4.1 But when I try to run
