>  > Control 0x72: +/80/160 C [Gamma - 1.8] 
>  > /home/common/resources/psychodelic_green2pink.ddcc
>  > Writing (...)
>  > _
>
> If this could be done, the election of pci or i2c wouldn't be important for 
> responsiveness.
>   
Yes... That sort of thing would be absolutely great... And it shouldn't
be really hard to do (if you look at ddccontrol main program, it is
really small), so, if somebody has the time to do this...

Best regards,

Nicolas


